snippet.title: NIBEOS, A VISUAL NOVEL, COMING SOON...
snippet.description:
Have you ever entered the lost time beyond midnight?
Do you ever walk at night alone through dark streets or wondered what does?
Have you ever felt secure in the deep shadows of night?
Or have you been awake in the depths of night staring at the darkness of a room?

This will be a story of that dark world which consumes our own every day for hours while most sleep, the story of its hunts, and its hunter...

Discord: https://discord.gg/HTx4FKQPGS 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Argonbolt
